Why CC BY 4.0?

This project incorporates content from two sources:

  1. "Elevation of Privilege" card game by Adam Shostack / Fraser Scott /
     Microsoft, released under CC BY 3.0.
     https://github.com/adamshostack/eop

  2. "LINDDUN GO" (2024) card game by DistriNet, KU Leuven, released
     under CC BY 4.0.
     https://linddun.org/go/

Both upstream sources are CC-BY (attribution only, no share-alike).
We therefore distribute the combined project under CC BY 4.0, which is
compatible with both. See ATTRIBUTION.md for full credits.
